## Case Study 3: Volkswagen (Full Network Down)

| Parameter    | Details                              |
| ------------ | ------------------------------------ |
| Vehicle type | VW MQB platform                      |
| Complaint    | No start, no scan tool communication |

### Diagnostic Table

| Step           | Finding                       |
| -------------- | ----------------------------- |
| OBD port test  | No response                   |
| CAN resistance | 0 Ω (short circuit)           |
| Isolation test | Removing ABS ECU restores bus |

### Root Cause

| Issue                                    | Result                  |
| ---------------------------------------- | ----------------------- |
| Faulty ABS module shorted CAN_H to CAN_L | Entire network collapse |

### Fix

| Action                 | Result                |
| ---------------------- | --------------------- |
| ABS module replacement | Full network recovery |

